languages.text: "Не грехами. Подвигами. Я много служил, чтобы добиться этой чести. Умолял. И получил".
"Not offences. Labours. I toiled to be granted this honour. I begged for it. And I received it."

languages.text: 「悪く思うなよ。俺はこの栄誉を得るために努力した。懇願し、そして入手したんだ」
languages.original_text: "Not offences. Labours. I toiled to be granted this honour. I begged for it. And I received it."

traits.locale_text: 「悪く思うなよ。俺はこの栄誉を得るために努力した。懇願し、そして入手したんだ」
traits.speaker: WrackServant

languages.text: “不是犯错，而是劳作。我辛苦劳作，才得到了这样的荣誉。我乞求主人赐予我他的礼物，他答应了。”
languages.original_text: "Not offences. Labours. I toiled to be granted this honour. I begged for it. And I received it."

traits.locale_text: “不是犯错，而是劳作。我辛苦劳作，才得到了这样的荣誉。我乞求主人赐予我他的礼物，他答应了。”
traits.speaker: WrackServant

languages.text: «Transgresiones no. Trabajos. Trabajé duro para que se me concediera este honor. Lo supliqué. Y lo recibí».
languages.original_text: "Not offences. Labours. I toiled to be granted this honour. I begged for it. And I received it."

traits.locale_text: «Transgresiones no. Trabajos. Trabajé duro para que se me concediera este honor. Lo supliqué. Y lo conseguí».
traits.speaker: WrackServant

languages.text: "Nicht Vergehen. Arbeiten. Ich habe geschuftet, um diese Ehre gewährt zu bekommen. Ich habe darum gebettelt. Und ich habe sie empfangen."
languages.original_text: "Not offences. Labours. I toiled to be granted this honour. I begged for it. And I received it."

traits.locale_text: "Nicht Vergehen. Arbeiten. Ich habe geschuftet, um diese Ehre gewährt zu bekommen. Ich habe darum gebettelt. Und ich habe sie erhalten."
traits.speaker: WrackServant

languages.text: « Aucun crime. C'est le fruit de mon travail. J'ai travaillé dur pour avoir cet honneur. J'ai supplié pour qu'on me l'accorde. Et on me l'a accordé. »
languages.original_text: "Not offences. Labours. I toiled to be granted this honour. I begged for it. And I received it."

languages.text: "Suç işlemedim. Emek harcadım. Bu onurun bana bahşedilmesi için çabaladım, yalvardım ve hak ettim."
